00:20:17.290 --> 00:20:20.270
if I use that here, gnarly
set of governance issues,

00:20:20.270 --> 00:20:23.840
how you have a shared data
structure, a shared ledger.

00:20:23.840 --> 00:20:26.210
And then, of course,
